flowchart TD
  START([ha_light_task_start]) --> Q[ha_light_cmd_queue · lamp_nvs_load]
  Q --> LOOP{{for ;;}}

  LOOP --> BOOT{led_is_booting?}
  BOOT -->|ano| W10[WDT · delay 10 ms] --> LOOP
  BOOT -->|ne| WDT[WDT reset]

  WDT --> RECV{xQueueReceive 100 ms}
  RECV -->|WEB_LAMP| LAMP[stav RGB · NVS · přepnutí HA mód]
  RECV -->|ACTIVITY| ACT[last_activity · GAME mód · MQTT event rate-limit]
  RECV -->|timeout| IDLE[pokračovat další logikou tasku]
  LAMP --> LOOP
  ACT --> LOOP
  IDLE --> LOOP
